  "description": "This individual is a human undead of spare, desiccated build, reduced to taut brown skin drawn hard over prominent bone. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets beneath a heavy brow ridge, giving the face a hollowed, sepulchral cast. Black hair persists in thin, uneven strands with a patchy scalp that exposes old abrasion marks. The jawline shows pitted fractures that have knit wrongly, fixing the mouth into a permanent, rigid asymmetry.",
